   - `toACCSystemCharges : ACCSystemCharges`: The underlying charge system (implicitly part of the structure due to extension).

2. **`χ.LinSols`**: A structure representing solutions to the linear ACCs:
   - `val : χ.1.Charges`: The underlying charge (where `χ.1 : ACCSystemCharges`).
