We need to show that for any `S T : χ.LinSols`, if `(χ.linSolsIncl) S = (χ.linSolsIncl) T`, then `S = T`.

But `(χ.linSolsIncl) S = S.val` and `(χ.linSolsIncl) T = T.val`, so the hypothesis becomes `S.val = T.val`.

